- **Substantial Holder:** First Sentier Investors RQI Pty Ltd (ACN 133 312 017) / Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group (MUFG) (indirect parent)  
- **Date of Becoming Substantial Holder:** 20/06/2025  
- **Total Voting Power:** 5.27% in Fleetpartners Group Ltd (via 11,831,463 fully paid ordinary shares)

- **Nature of Interest:** Control via investment mandates (Corporations Act 608(1)(b)/(c))  
- **Key Associates:** Multiple First Sentier/MUFG subsidiaries (see Annexure A)  

*No material trading or capital markets impact identified (disclosure only).*
